.SH OTHER OPTIONS
.BI "-[no]h"  "    no"
 Print help info and quit

.BI "-nice"  " int" " 19" 
 Set the nicelevel

.BI "-b"  " time" "     -1" 
 First frame (ps) to read from trajectory

.BI "-e"  " time" "     -1" 
