.BI "-dt"  " time" "     -1" 
 Only use frame when t MOD dt = first time (ps)

.BI "-tu"  " enum" " ps" 
 Time unit: 
.B ps
, 
.B fs
, 
.B ns
, 
.B us
, 
.B ms
, 
